## 2. Folder Structure

```
apps/web/
├── app/                          # Next.js App Router — routing ONLY
│   └── [workspace]/
│       ├── (admin)/              # Route group: authenticated admin routes
│       │   ├── products/
│       │   │   └── page.tsx      # Thin shell: imports from features/products
│       │   └── layout.tsx        # AuthGuard + DashboardLayout
│       └── (superadmin)/
